                        <p class="mb-4">
                            Currently, I'm exploring various aspects of AI including natural language processing, 
                            computer vision, and machine learning algorithms. I believe in learning by doing, 
                            which is why I'm constantly working on projects that challenge my understanding and 
                            push the boundaries of what I can create.
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="skills-list">
                            <h4 class="mb-3">What I'm Learning:</h4>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
